<p>Want to learn how to stream DVDs to your iPad? Want to fix your Mail rules so that they stick from launch to launch? How about clearing up ghost messages in Mail that just <em>won&rsquo;t</em> delete? Or maybe you want to learn how to remove Google&rsquo;s software update from your Mac? This and more is what other Mac Geek Gab listeners have asked about, and John F. Braun and Dave Hamilton have your answers.&nbsp;All of this and more in today&rsquo;s Premium episode of Mac Geek Gab. Subscribe for 6 months (it&rsquo;s just US$25) and enjoy!</p>
